Welcome to pmcenter 2.0!

pmcenter now depends on .NET Core 3.1, with these enhancements and new features:
[/] Backend code refactor
[/] Now pmcenter turns on Message Links by default
[+] NuGet package updates
[+] HTTP/2 protocol support
[+] Dices & darts support
[+] Inline keyboard actions support
[+] R2R + AOT packages available via GitHub releases
[+] Startup time analysis
[+] Toggleable autosave
[+] Better forwarding logics
[+] JSON configuration files can be minified
[+] Language version mismatch check is now toggleable

[+] 优化的转发逻辑
[+] JSON 配置文件现可最小化
[+] 可开关语言文件版本匹配警告
